UBA Mortgage

The UBA Mortgage is a two-in-one product designed to offer:

Mortgage Loan - credit facilities to part finance applicants’ acquisition of residential property in locations acceptable to the Bank; and

Home Equity Loan - loans to applicants against the value of existing residential property in acceptable locations

Eligibility

  • Employees of blue chip companies and reputable audit, law and consulting firms as well as banks and insurance companies.
  • Employees of international Organizations, Reputable NGOs etc. Civil Servants

Features

  • Mortgage Loan: 80% of total cost of property
  • Home Equity Loan: 75% of the value of property
  • Tenor: Up to 20 years

Benefits

  • Enables customers to own their own residential houses now and pay for it over a long period of time
  • Provides customers with one more option for growing their wealth using existing assets
